        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2801825270" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer129274124670981069"><b>3 Stars</b> - Good book <br/><br/>This book is quintessentially cozy to me. I wanted it to be a cool fall day, so I could curl up with this book and a pot of tea in a big, comfy chair. I felt as if I lived alongside the characters. <br/><br/>Other reviews are out there that do a better job at describing this book than I can so I’ll let you read their reviews. <br/><br/>Do I recommend this one? Yes, I think I do. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


