              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3790324691280988767">Maeve Binchy is a wonderful story teller. This is along complicated family tale. Her characters are so real that you can reach out and touch them. I recommend Maeve Binchy to whomever wants to be lost in a book.</span>

          </span>
